    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Genus containing around about 40 species of trees and succulent shrubs native primarily to Africa, but also found in Asia and Central America. In earlier classifications, placed in family Agavaceae.</Note_Text>
